      "translation": "AIA has a long and storied history in Asia. Having navigated various social upheavals and uncertain periods while managing our business prudently, we have earned a distinguished reputation reflecting our trustworthiness, resilience and strength, and commitment to doing right by our stakeholders. Since early 2020, the COVID-19 pandemic has created continuously evolving and increasingly complex business environments, while political, macroeconomic and capital market landscapes have undergone unprecedented shifts. In this context, AIA's financial strength and our mission to \"help people live healthier, longer, better lives\" are more significant than ever. I am deeply grateful to all AIA employees, agents and partners who, despite severe challenges, continue to care for our communities, fulfill their responsibilities diligently, and dedicate themselves to supporting our customers, their families and our communities."
